#X text 367 491 since the midi clock goes to all 16 channels there isn't any need to set a particular channel;
#X text 446 -3 the top section here is pretty much all from the abl_link~ example. I added a couple more buttons to the division link that give different subdivisions of the tempo to have stuff play at half speed/double speed etc. To accommodate faster subdivisions I added a bunch of numbers in the sel object below. I bet there is a nicer way to do this. If you wanna go EVEN FASTER then add more numbers. The way I have this hooked up \, it only controls the audio output. Maybe someone will know how to have it affect the midi clock out too.;
